Package: DPMirt
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Semiparametric Item Response Theory Models Using Dirichlet
    Process Mixture Priors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("JoonHo", "Lee", , "jlee296@ua.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits Bayesian semiparametric Item Response Theory (IRT) models
    using Dirichlet Process Mixture (DPM) priors via NIMBLE. Supports Rasch,
    2PL, and 3PL models with both parametric (Normal) and semiparametric (DPM)
    latent trait priors. Provides multiple posterior summary methods including
    posterior mean (PM), constrained Bayes (CB; Ghosh, 1992), and triple-goal
    (GR; Shen & Louis, 1998) estimators. Features a compile-once, sample-many
    workflow for efficient MCMC computation, built-in simulation tools, and
    comprehensive diagnostics.
